      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable and practical vehicle that's ready to hit the road? This car is in fair condition, showing some honest signs of use and character from its time on the move, but it still has plenty of life left! It\u2019s a dependable choice for anyone needing a solid daily driver that balances value and utility perfectly.",
