    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is an exemplary specimen of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom-grade condition, exhibiting flawless exterior surfaces and an interior cabin that retains its original factory integrity. Mechanically, the unit performs to exacting standards, offering a driving experience indistinguishable from its initial delivery. This represents a rare opportunity for the sophisticated collector to acquire a vehicle maintained with uncompromising attention to detail.",
